article.description: — Lagio Grantsaan tossed in 19 points, De'Torrion Ware scored 17 and Morgan State rolled to an 82-48 victory over Maryland-Eastern Shore on Monday night.
article.headline: Grantsaan, Ware spark Morgan State to 82-48 romp over UMES
article.linkText: Grantsaan, Ware spark Morgan State to 82-48 romp over UMES
article.story: BALTIMORE -- — Lagio Grantsaan tossed in 19 points, De'Torrion Ware scored 17 and Morgan State rolled to an 82-48 victory over Maryland-Eastern Shore on Monday night. Malik Miller added 14 points and seven rebounds for the Bears (11-13, 6-6 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference). Sherwyn Devonish had six assists. Da'Shawn Phillip had 10 points for the Hawks (10-14, 5-8). Nathaniel Pollard Jr. added seven rebounds. The Bears evened the season series against the Hawks. Maryland Eastern Shore defeated Morgan State 79-72 on Jan. 31. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ Portions of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
